$ Create a Message Box with PowerShell

The following example tries to demonstrate how the → Windows/development/WinAPI function `MessageBox` (defined in → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/user32_dll[`user32.dll`])
can be called from → Windows/PowerShell.

